            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-body prose">
          <p class="intro">Hello, I'm Kai.</p>
          
          <p>
            I am a Software Engineer at Google based in New York City, currently working on 
            post-training for <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2507.06261" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gemini</a>. 
            I have focused on enhancing model performance in factuality, grounding, multi-turn 
            reasoning, and visual search. I have landed improvements across SFT, RL, Reward Models 
            and Evals. Before joining the Gemini team, I researched retrieval-enhanced transformer 
            architectures.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Prior to that, I was part of Google Research, where I spent a year and a half trying to 
            understand US Healthcare IT infrastructure. I built ingestion tools for <a href="https://github.com/google/bulk_fhir_tools" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FHIR Bulk Data APIs</a>, 
            a <a href="https://github.com/google/cql" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clinical Quality Language</a> (CQL) execution engine for analyzing healthcare data at scale, 
            and infrastructure for <a href="https://blog.google/technology/health/take-look-conditions-our-new-feature-care-studio/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Care Studio</a>, a nice UI for electronic health records.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            I received an undergraduate degree from the University of Alberta.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you are in NYC and would like to chat over coffee feel free to reach out to kaibailey44 [at] gmail [dot] com.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .main {
    flex: 1;
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(12px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  .about-header {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .profile-image {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  [data-theme="dark"] .profile-image {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .profile-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .profile-info h1 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
  
  .role {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .social-links a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .social-links a:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  
  .about-body .intro {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .profile-image {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
    
    .social-links {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
